title: VA portal of perceptions (celestial dragon records)
description:
Mastering by Huby Sea and Vincent Villuis
Artwork by Quasga 
  
  
  1. Ephemeral mists - venus

  3. Adham Shaikh - Ohm (Transfix Mix) 
   Featuring Gemma Luna vox, Miroslav: Fuijara. Written by Adham Shaikh 
     
  4. Aes Dana - Haze (Celestial Mix) 
   Written and produced by Vincent Villuis 
     
  5. Androcell - Carribeyond 
   Written and produced by Tyler Smith  
     
  6. Cell - Twisted Sun 
   Written and produced by Alex Scheffer at Atmospheric Studio, Paris 
     
  7. Androcell - Fungus Garden (Acoustic Mix) 
   Written and Produced by Tyler Smith  
     
  8. H.U.V.A. Network - Rain Geometries (Solar Fields Remix) 
    Original track written and produced by Vincent Villuis and Magnus 
Birgersson. Additional production by Magnus Birgersson 
      
  9. Ishq - El Morya 
    Written by Ishq and recorded at Thx1138 Cornwall, UK
